name: Large Blue & White Ticking Cushion
description:
Large cotton ticking cushion in classic blue & white, just perfect for complimenting any country style interior - comes complete with quality feather insert.

Size: 55cm x 55cm

name: Vintage Chemistry Apothecary Bottle
description:
This large vintage glass bottle, made by the glassware manufacturers Pyrex, is in lovely condition and has been previously used in the chemistry lab for distilled water... 
It stands 9" tall, and has a tapered glass stopper.
We have applied our Permillion label (because we love it so much!) to add to the aesthetic appeal, but this can be easily removed if you wish.

name: Luxury Handmade Soy Candle
description:
Our classic, handmade, pure soy scented candles, are a natural way to gently enhance the ambiance of your home - simply light the cotton wick and relax!

The No.44 scent is a subtle and delicate fragrance, with the warm and woody undertones of Sandalwood, mixed with invigorating aromas of Bergumont - just gorgeous!

The No.7 scent is a sultry aromatic fragrance, just perfect for an evening of relaxation, with hints of White Musk and the rich undertones of Amber. 

Supplied in a quality milskin black presentation box.

Burn Time: approx. 36 hours.
Net Weight: 240g

name: Small Vintage Glass Bottles (Calcium Acetate, Ol. Ricini, Sacchar)
description:
The bottles are in beautiful vintage condition for their age, with no chips or cracks -they have original chemists labels applied to them and although not original to the bottle, we feel this adds to their eclectic style. 

Dimensions:
Calcium Acetate; 12cm
Ol. Ricini; 14cm
Sacchar; 7cm

name: Heritage Tweed Wool Cushion
description:
This gorgeous wool tweed cushion is that perfect addition to your country style interior, in pale dusky greens and pinks with plain twill backing and complete with a plump feather insert, its just the thing to cosy up with these chill winter evenings!!

Size: 55cm X 55cm

name: Vintage Underwood Typewriter
description: A style icon, this is a perfect addition to any modern or vintage style interior - with it's clickety clicks & nostalgic dings, these pieces of kit are always a favourite. It is in working condition but could probably benefit from a new ribbon if it was intended for use...

name: Wooden Ruler
description: 19th Century Boxwood Rabone ruler with brass hinges and detailing, with a beautiful aged patina. Rabone were the Creme De la Creme of craftsmanship, the numbers and measurements are still well defined, making them as usable now as when they were first purchased.

name: Handcrafted Aran Wool Cushion
description:
Perfect for dressing up your favourite sofa, these stunning cable cushion covers are hand knitted with pure Aran wool - they have been hand finished with a gorgeous richly coloured Union Jack patch and three wooden buttons - a must for the coming winter evenings!
Available in Charcoal Grey or Soft Pale Grey...
Supplied with a quality feather insert.

Size 16" x 16"

name: Vintage Wood and Brass Surveyors Tripod Lamp
description:
A stylish example of an authentic vintage Surveyors Theodolite Tripod, sympathetically converted into a unique modern floor-standing lamp. The fittings have been chosen to compliment the age and quality of this eye-catching piece, including modern three-core braided flex. 

With intricate brass findings, and waxed & stained wooden legs, this is a true 'one-off'!

*Because of shipping difficulties, this is sold without the shade.

name: Small Vintage Framed Butterfly
description: This rare, vintage butterfly specimen has some age to it, but has been beautifully preserved within its box frame - a must for any entomologist or budding naturalist!

name: Large Country Tweed Cushion
description:
Perfect for cosying up with on a chilly winters evening, this gorgeous  tweed cushion in dark heather and soft complimentary tones has a soft woollen front with plain twill backing - comes complete with quality plump feather insert. Country style at its best!

Size: 55cm x 55cm

name: Industrial Coffee Table
description:
Reclaimed vintage cart-style coffee table with black cast-iron original Slingsby wheels -this is an extremely sturdy (and very heavy!) statement piece of furniture that would look equally at home in a period property or modern interior. 
It is in vintage condition with gentle 'knocks and dings', that only serve to add to the character of this bold statement piece. 

Dimensions:
Width; 81cm
Length; 119cm
Height; 32cm

***This is a hefty piece, weighing in at more than 40kgs, so regrettably we can not ship internationally. For UK shipping, please contact us prior to purchasing with your location, and we will source the best delivery service for you. Many Thanks!

name: Large Classic Leather Case
description:
A gorgeous vintage large leather case with leather interior and 'product pockets and slots' - the case has seen some use over the years and has gained some scars to bear witness to this, but nothing that detracts; it has been given a coat of wax to bring out the dark tan patina and is all ready to add instant character to your home.

*This is made of thick, substantial leather and as such, weighs quite a considerable amount.

name: Cast Iron Coat Hooks (Set of 3 Hooks available)
description: A staple of any home, these vintage coat hooks have been mounted on a reclaimed wooden plinth, also with a french enamel number plaque to add to the vintage feel. With fixings, this piece comes ready to hang!

name: Vintage Topographical Map
description: This map is an original British RAF Ministry of Defence piece of history, dated 1965 - it is a large 41.5" x 57"and would be perfect for a plain white wall or to put in an elegant over-sized frame for a vintage feel to a modern environment.

name: Vintage Camera - USSR Fed 3
description: This vintage USSR camera is in gorgeous condition and comes with its original leather case, it would make a fine addition to any camera collection! - the shutter and shooting pin seem to be working fine but it has not been film or light tested.

name: Steamer Trunk
description:
A unique and beautiful vintage domed topped steamer trunk;  this would be as equally at home in a period property or a modern interior with an eclectic edge.
 It has it's original leather handles to both sides and metal detailing, lined with pages of Latin text, this gorgeous trunk has any number of uses; as a blanket box, in the boot room or simply as a toy chest in a playroom, as versatile as you want to make it!

Dimensions; 
Length 76.5cm
Width 59cm
Height; 61 cm

*Due to the size & weight, unfortunately this item can not be shipped Internationally.

description:
This is a must for the avid crafter out there, we have available the pictured lead type blocks in the font shown; we have the letters A-Z in limited numbers and also the corresponding numbers 0-9, plus various punctuation and ampersand's.

We have shown them next to a ruler to show the approximate size, with the larger being just under an inch, and the smaller being just over half an inch.  

Please contact us before ordering to let us know what letters and the size you would require.

*Shipping costs will be dependent on amount purchased as the type is lead so subsequently is fairly heavy.

description: This is a truly impressive pair of floor standing lamps, they have been converted from original Surveyors Tripods - made from stained oak with brass components, these are craftsmanship at it's best...things are just not made like this anymore!! Standing an imposing 6' in height they would make a beautiful statement piece in any room! The light fittings have been matched to compliment the age and quality of the tripods, with modern black 3 core braided flex cable & aged brass fittings that complete the unique ambience of these eye catching, unique pieces of furniture.
